      "acceptanceCriteria": "Software must be verified under a formal QA plan with documented unit and integration tests traceable to requirements; version control and change control required at MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver (OpenFOAM v9) is under version control and has documented regression tests. However, the hemolysis scalar transport sub-model lacks independent unit-test coverage, and the QA plan does not formally trace hemolysis model requirements to test cases. Achieved level 3; required level 4 for MRL 5."
