      "acceptanceCriteria": "The hemolysis constitutive model (power-law form) must be evaluated against alternatives; model-form uncertainty must be quantified and propagated to NIH predictions.",
      "rationale": "Only the Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law hemolysis model was used. No comparison against the Arora or Taskin models was performed. Model-form uncertainty was not quantified. Factor not-assessed at MRL 5."
